WHEREAS, Patricia Ann McKinney Pendergrass leaves a lasting legacy of faith,
love, compassion, and determination and will be greatly missed by all whose lives she
touched.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby express sincere and heartfelt condolences to the family and friends of Patricia
Ann McKinney Pendergrass.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to the
family of Patricia Ann McKinney Pendergrass.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
